  <h5 class="text-center">Chance, pictured looking down at his daughter on his album cover, has been an intergral part of improving the conditions of Chicago, and raising moral of the citizens</h5>

  <ul>
    <li><b>April 16, 1993</b> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chance_the_Rapper">Chancelor Bennit</a> was born</li>
