    <li><b>April 30, 2013</b> Acid Rap was released</li>
    <li><b>May 28, 2015</b> Surf was co-released with Donnie Trumpet</li>
    <li><b>May 13, 2016</b> Chance's third project Coloring Book was released. Coloring Book went under the alias "C3" until the title and artwork were revealed</li>

    <li><b>September 18, 2016</b> Chance welcomed his daughter into the world</li>
